# Module Workflows

This project has detailed workflows for publishing and installing Aether modules. **Do not proceed without explicit user confirmation.**

- **Publishing** (package a feature from `features/` into `packages/`, publish to GitHub Packages): read and follow `.cursor/commands/publish_module.md`
- **Installing** (install from GitHub Packages, configure `nuxt.config.ts`, clear caches): read and follow `.cursor/commands/install_module.md`

Never auto-execute these workflows just because trigger phrases were mentioned. If the user is asking questions, answer them. Only run the workflow after explicit confirmation.
